"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642001825,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"l68L0fDE_q1AfakGZAmMrDl5KuQNJuuiULCkjqKjXZU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe8a851cFe77caB145780627d09D3A6d0C5530db5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N-GkBf9soxFkpk4OZO3cCMgvuP8Bu76fSffn7M6zdGk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"TtdZRB9sppPhEt0WhNsOGay-AMQBG87fsXG3gsB1ROU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"TlIVw3QlRwJxAEVdgyXw02kG4vRppwyq1k-UNc8Mo8xYK3NUa14StJj4rjobaftFH25oebeJhegPrQrMnFwdgQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x82642f47a13cfa8073d3811899e4097d8cb1f877e3e5692bdcfb7195cc95978f48bcb9ec0e61e055b43844e1d5349164e2052fa52678f96f3dfdd2a1bfece2fe1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N-GkBf9soxFkpk4OZO3cCMgvuP8Bu76fSffn7M6zdGk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"TtdZRB9sppPhEt0WhNsOGay-AMQBG87fsXG3gsB1ROU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi